Use in VSC - Ctrl + Shift + P  and type: "Open Keyboard Shortcuts (JSON)"

and paste there this json:

[
    {
        "key": "ctrl+shift+right",
        "command": "cursorColumnSelectRight",
        "when": "textInputFocus"
    },
    {
        "key": "ctrl+shift+left",
        "command": "cursorColumnSelectLeft",
        "when": "textInputFocus"
    },
    {
        "key": "ctrl+shift+up",
        "command": "cursorColumnSelectUp",
        "when": "textInputFocus"
    },
    {
        "key": "ctrl+shift+down",
        "command": "cursorColumnSelectDown",
        "when": "textInputFocus"
    }
]
